data.description: Look no further! This is it! This beautiful fully updated home in Westview is 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with KILLER natural light. The open concept home allows you to flow perfectly from the living room, to the dining room, kitchen and out towards the professionally landscaped backyard with shed. The primary suite has two closets and boasts a double vanity and double shower heads in the en suite bathroom. The kitchen has a perfect island for your guests to sit while you're finishing up the meal. The oven is a convection oven so it shouldn't be too much longer before dinner is ready! This has a roommate floor plan with the secondary bedrooms and bathroom in a private space off of the dining room. The outdoor space is an urban oasis as you see the plants line the fence and the wonderfully green grass throughout. But don't forget about the front porch! This lot is zoned r4 so you could put an ADU in the back. Walkable to Slutty Vegan, Plant Lady Juice, BBQ, Pinchos and the westside Atlanta BeltLine.
